  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 180°C.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together the flour, melted butter, and beaten eggs.",
    "Add the chopped onion, minced garlic, and grated carrot to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Add the trimmed green beans and stir to combine.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 20x20cm baking dish.",
    "Pour in the hot beef stock and milk, and stir to combine.",
    "Sprinkle the grated parmesan cheese on top of the mixture.",
    "Cover the dish with aluminum foil and bake for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the foil and continue baking for a further 20 minutes, or until the top is golden brown and the mixture is set."
  ],
